Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.03,0:01:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附近都没有契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在没有契约者的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.00,0:01:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好几个灵体一起出现…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还真有点异常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.42,0:01:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 艾丽丝?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忽然脸色都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.61,0:02:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 奥兹!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉贝优…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.27,0:02:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首都在燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H666666&\b0\pos(319,372)\blur7}同情的赞歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.43,0:02:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再快点 基尔!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵体的总攻?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前所未有的惊人数量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么灵体们忽然发狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即派出镇压部队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让潘多拉所有力量到拉贝优集合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首都很快就会毁灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扑克牌怎么会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.27,0:03:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装填!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准眉间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在 快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是巴司卡瓦干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不觉得是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也没有能做到这步的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底原因是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿嵬茨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿嵬茨的意志…在悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是阿嵬茨的意志?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道 就是有种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝是通过直觉感受到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿嵬茨的意志的异变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以阿嵬茨的平衡才破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了 基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管感到荣幸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我染血黑兔大人怎么超度你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也来战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾克列斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的孩子还在屋子里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里 在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 没事了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到你妈妈那里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖孩子 乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去安全的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有考虑到你的体力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太乱来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还能战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 你这个病号
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:08:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 虽说是些杂牌灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还有五万只呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管打倒多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍然源源不断地出现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潘多拉总部在干些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是极限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来是很期待奥兹的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认真一点好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疯帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑 艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量远离疯帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:10:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否定并销毁一切与阿嵬茨相关事物的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵体全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人吃惊的威力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找基尔他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿嵬茨的异变还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屋子里的人都去避难了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来火堆这边吧 艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是让人讨厌的景色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像阿嵬茨一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被孤独和绝望支配的黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一天一天地过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整天跟灵体作无意义的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身心都像冰一般寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到你这个仆人出现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿嵬茨是比死亡更可怕的无间地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿嵬茨的平衡破坏的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是因为阿嵬茨的意志也很寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也像艾丽丝一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在孤独与绝望中悲鸣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是风罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴司卡瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里昂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是来救我们的吗 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是服从命令罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要制止现在阿嵬茨发生的异状
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要奥兹·贝萨流士的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的力量?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就交给我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是别忘了 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次见面之时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们就是敌人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有子弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潘多拉的增援部队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.09,0:15:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你们没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友军的灵体一下子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次使用疯帽子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能把那怪物…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那副身体再使用力量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹 体力恢复了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们是逃不过阿嵬茨的考验了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海藻头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次解放染血黑兔的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是他的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 这是我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这只臭鸟!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要制止现在阿嵬茨发生的异状
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要奥兹·贝萨流士的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许现在的你还没有意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 只有你拥有解开一切谜团 知晓真相的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.61,0:17:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有控制阿嵬茨一切的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想出一份力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我真的有那样的力量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要告别了 艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是最后一次陪你玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的是?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:18:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵体拥有的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所失去的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要告别了 艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是最后一次陪你玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要告别
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远在我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.23,0:19:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你 求求你了 杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的声音 传到了阿嵬茨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传给了另一个我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制阿嵬茨的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 脸色很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候 我感觉到了恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要被灵体杀掉的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是就这样死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.55,0:20:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅不知道自己是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也见不到艾丽丝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次我从内心感受到了「要活下去」的意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的你 总是借着自我牺牲的名义轻视自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只有感觉到恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人才会变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收回哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前说你是令人恐惧的小鬼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你的过去充满悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.51,0:21:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你充满了痛苦之时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会全心全意去接受你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.26,0:21:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.91,0:22:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭你仆人的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不等你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹 你别得意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.03,0:23:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}父亲 不在了……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.36,0:23:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}我到底是什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.62,0:23:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}为什么总是要被否定!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.33,0:23:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}很想见一面吧 小鬼?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}我是个满身缺点的人……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.50,0:24:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}你若是不被别人认同的话——
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.68,0:24:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}不能存在吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.80,0:24:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&}下回 向着否定的前方